Clint has been great to work with.  His initial vision for our backyard blew us away.  Then, he created something that was even better than his renderings.  He continues to check in on us to make sure everything is going well.  Clint has been super!

Clint was a pleasure to work with. Value and quality were excellent. I had ten estimates and went with Clint who was recommend from a co worker and friend. Any issues during or after were handled quickly. On top of this he is a really good person.  Thinking of doing a spa next year and will be going to Clint to have it done. :) More
